export const questionObj = {"Qtext": "
 
Suppose that 
\[
	\frac{a }{k } = \frac{b }{l } = \frac{c }{m }
\]
Then show that each ratio is equal to
\[
	\left(\frac{3 a ^3 - 5 b ^3 + 3 c ^3}{3 k ^3 - 5 l ^3 + 3 m ^3}\right)^{1/3}
\]
\newline

", "Steps": [{"id": "s1", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "It is given that 
\[
	\frac{a }{k } = \frac{b }{b } = \frac{c }{m } = n \textrm{ assume}
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow a = kn , b = ln , c = mn 
\]
Given expression is
\[
	\left(\frac{3 a ^3 - 5 b ^3 + 3 c ^3}{3 k ^3 - 5 l ^3 + 3 m ^3}\right)^{1/3}
\]
\[
	= \left(\frac{3 n ^3 k ^3 - 5 n ^3 l ^3 + 3 n ^3 m ^3}{3 k ^3 - 5 l ^3 + 3 m ^3}\right)^{1/3}
\]
\[
	\left(\frac{n ^3 (3 k ^3 - 5 l ^3 + 3 m ^3)}{3 k ^3 - 5 l ^3 + 3 m ^3}\right)^{1/3}
\]
\[
	= (n ^3)^{1/3}
\]
\[
	= n 
\]
Which is equal to each ratio.

Hence proved.
\newline

"}]} 

 export const resp = [{"data": [], "text": " "}]
